Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:02.45,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(489,0)}I've still got a lot of years ahead of me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.41,0:01:04.46,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\pos(640,700)}{\alpha&HFF&}To just erase these fee{\alpha&H00&}lings?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.37,0:01:04.41,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\pos(640,700)}{\alpha&HFF&}To just erase {\alpha&H00&}these feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.45,0:01:04.37,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\pos(640,700)}To just erase these feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.83,0:01:07.46,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(489,0)}I want to go back and finish
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.46,0:01:11.09,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,489)}The things that I've yet to finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.14,0:01:27.35,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(489,489)}I was supposed to be chasing after my ongoing dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.85,0:01:33.69,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(489,0)}Yet I faltered over others while walking this thin, winding path.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.69,0:01:36.86,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}It's not that I want to return to those days.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.86,0:01:40.37,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'm searching for the sky I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.37,0:01:42.03,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Don't make that sad face, as if you've fallen victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.03,0:01:47.25,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}As if you want people to pity you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.25,0:01:48.96,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Tears aren't the end of your sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.96,0:01:50.63,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You have to bear them painfully, forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.63,0:01:52.29,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Who are you waiting for in the maze of emotions,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.29,0:01:53.96,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Where you can't even see the exit?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.96,0:01:55.76,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I want to blurt it out more justly,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.76,0:01:57.51,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Just like how I wrote it in my white notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.51,0:01:59.18,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}What do you want to run from?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.18,0:02:00.80,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}That thing called "reality"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:04.14,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I just want to scream out,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.14,0:02:07.56,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}"I'm only living to fulfill my wish." Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.56,0:02:11.69,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,489)}I can't take the safe way out of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:14.48,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I don't even have a place to return to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.48,0:02:17.78,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'm always thankful for everyone's kindness,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.78,0:02:21.16,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}That's why I want to become stronger. (I'm on the way)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.16,0:02:23.12,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}This is reminding me of the old days.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:26.37,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,889)}This pain is all right with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:02.45,OP01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(489,0)}{\blur3}この想いを　消してしまうには
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.41,0:01:04.46,OP01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\pos(644,652)}{\alpha&HFF&}まだ人生長いでし{\alpha&H00&}ょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.37,0:01:04.41,OP01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\pos(644,652)}{\alpha&HFF&}まだ人生{\alpha&H00&}長いでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.45,0:01:04.37,OP01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\pos(644,652)}まだ人生長いでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.83,0:01:07.46,OP01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(489,0)}やり残してるコト
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.46,0:01:11.09,OP01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,489)}やり直してみたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.14,0:01:27.35,OP01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(489,489)}夢のつづき　追いかけていたはずなのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.85,0:01:33.69,OP01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(489,0)}曲がりくねった　細い道　人につまずく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.69,0:01:36.86,OP01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}あの頃みたいにって　戻りたい訳じゃないの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.86,0:01:40.37,OP01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}無くしてきた空を　探してる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.37,0:01:42.03,OP01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}わかってくれますように
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.03,0:01:47.25,OP01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}犠牲になったような　悲しい顔はやめてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.25,0:01:48.96,OP01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}罪の最後は涙じゃないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.96,0:01:50.63,OP01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}ずっと苦しく背負ってくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.63,0:01:52.29,OP01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}出口見えない感情迷路に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.29,0:01:53.96,OP01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}誰を待ってるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.96,0:01:55.76,OP01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}白いノートに綴ったように
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.76,0:01:57.51,OP01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}もっと素直に吐き出したいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.51,0:01:59.18,OP01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}何から　逃れたいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.18,0:02:00.80,OP01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}…現実ってやつ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:04.14,OP01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}叶えるために　生きてるんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.14,0:02:07.56,OP01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}叫びたくなるよ　聞こえていますか？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.56,0:02:11.69,OP01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,489)}無難になんて　やってられないから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:14.48,OP01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}…帰る場所も無いの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.48,0:02:17.78,OP01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}優しさには　いつも感謝してる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.78,0:02:21.16,OP01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}だから強くなりたい{\alpha&HFF&}(I'm on the the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.78,0:02:21.16,OP01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\pos(820,652)}(I'm on the way)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.16,0:02:23.12,OP01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}懐かしくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:26.37,OP01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,889)}こんな痛みも歓迎じゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:02.45,OP01 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(489,0)}Kono omoi wo keshiteshimau niwa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.45,0:01:04.46,OP01 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Mada jinsei nagai desho?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.83,0:01:07.46,OP01 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(489,0)}Yarinokoshiteru koto
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.46,0:01:11.09,OP01 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,489)}Yarinaoshite mitai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.14,0:01:27.35,OP01 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(489,489)}Yume no tsuzuki oikaketeita hazu nanoni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.85,0:01:33.69,OP01 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(489,0)}Magarikunetta hosoi michi hito ni tsumazuku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.69,0:01:36.86,OP01 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Ano koro mitainitte modoritai wake ja nai no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.86,0:01:40.37,OP01 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Nakushitekita sora wo sagashiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.37,0:01:42.03,OP01 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Wakatte kuremasu youni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.03,0:01:47.25,OP01 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Gisei ni natta youna kanashii kao wa yameteyo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.25,0:01:48.96,OP01 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Tsumi no saigo wa namida ja nai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.96,0:01:50.63,OP01 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Zutto kurushiku seottekunda
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.63,0:01:52.29,OP01 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Deguchi mienai kanjoumeiro ni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.29,0:01:53.96,OP01 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Dare wo matteruno?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.96,0:01:55.76,OP01 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Shiroi nooto ni tsuzutta youni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.76,0:01:57.51,OP01 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Motto sunao ni hakidashitai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.51,0:01:59.18,OP01 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Nani kara nogaretainda
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.18,0:02:00.80,OP01 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Genjitsu tte yatsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:04.14,OP01 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Kanaeru tame ni ikiterundatte
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.14,0:02:07.56,OP01 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Sakebitaku naru yo kikoeteimasuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.56,0:02:11.69,OP01 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,489)}Bunan ni nante yatterarenaikara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:14.48,OP01 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Kaeru basho mo nai no
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.48,0:02:17.78,OP01 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Yasashisa ni wa itsumo kansha shiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.78,0:02:21.16,OP01 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Dakara tsuyoku naritai (I'm on the way)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.16,0:02:23.12,OP01 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Natsukashiku naru
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:26.37,OP01 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,889)}Konna itami mo kangei jan
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.74,0:22:33.24,ED01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(480,0)}Say, the sky we saw that day, the scarlet sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.24,0:22:38.46,ED01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Do you remember it from that day?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.46,0:22:44.38,ED01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}We made a promise and a vow while the early summer wind circled us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.38,0:22:48.63,ED01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,480)}And we clung close together.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.18,0:22:57.68,ED01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(480,0)}Your forced smile
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.68,0:23:03.06,ED01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Holds elongated shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.06,0:23:12.32,ED01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,480)}I pretend not to notice and continue on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.95,0:23:21.83,ED01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(480,480)}All the while waiting for you to deliver some news at the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.46,0:23:30.22,ED01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(480,0)}Empty nights, mornings that will never arrive,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.22,0:23:34.97,ED01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I could see them from a mile away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.97,0:23:40.60,ED01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Say, the sky we saw that day, the scarlet sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.60,0:23:45.52,ED01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'm sure you'll remember it one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.52,0:23:51.36,ED01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}While holding the promise we couldn't keep,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.36,0:23:55.62,ED01 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,480)}We take our first steps down our own paths.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.74,0:22:33.24,ED01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(480,0)}{\blur3}あの日見た空　茜色の空を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.24,0:22:38.46,ED01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}ねえ　君は覚えていますか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.46,0:22:44.38,ED01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}約束　契り　初夏の風が包む
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.38,0:22:48.63,ED01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,480)}二人　寄り添った
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.18,0:22:57.68,ED01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(480,0)}無理な笑顔の裏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.68,0:23:03.06,ED01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}伸びた影をかくまう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.06,0:23:12.32,ED01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,480)}だから　気づかぬふり　再生を選ぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.95,0:23:21.83,ED01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(480,480)}テーブルの上の　震えない知らせ　待ち続けて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.46,0:23:30.22,ED01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(480,0)}空白の夜も　来るはずのない朝も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.22,0:23:34.97,ED01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}全部わかってたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.97,0:23:40.60,ED01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}あの日見た空　茜色の空を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.60,0:23:45.52,ED01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}ねえ　 いつか思い出すでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.52,0:23:51.36,ED01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}果たせなかった　約束を抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.36,0:23:55.62,ED01 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,480)}二人　歩き出す
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.74,0:22:33.24,ED01 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(480,0)}Ano hi mita sora akaneiro no sora wo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.24,0:22:38.46,ED01 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Nee kimi wa oboeteimasuka
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.46,0:22:44.38,ED01 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Yakusoku chigiri shoka no kaze ga tsutsumu
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.38,0:22:48.63,ED01 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,480)}Futari yorisotta
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.18,0:22:57.68,ED01 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(480,0)}Muri na egao no ura
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.68,0:23:03.06,ED01 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Nobita kage wo kakumau
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.06,0:23:12.32,ED01 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,480)}Dakara kizukanu furi saisei wo erabu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.95,0:23:21.83,ED01 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(480,480)}Teeburu no ue no furuenai shirase machitsuzukete
