Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:24.46,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:28.17,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thankful you were in Central at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.17,0:00:29.88,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I can leave this to you without reservation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.80,0:00:33.92,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and that boy is here as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.92,0:00:36.05,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Utilize him to your liking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.05,0:00:39.56,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Führer President Bradley, by "boy", do you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.56,0:00:44.27,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The Fullmetal Alchemist, Edward Elric.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.81,0:00:48.27,Default,Edward,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, that Colonel is a slave driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:52.53,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,And we'd just bought a train ticket to Lior, too. Guess we're going to have to cancel that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.53,0:00:53.94,Default,Edward,0000,0000,0000,,Well, nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.65,0:00:57.32,Default,Edward,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get this over with quick, Al.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.32,0:00:58.78,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.84,0:02:35.34,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,There he is! That way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.34,0:02:36.84,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! If you don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.23,0:02:56.36,Default,Ice,0000,0000,0000,,Freezing and boiling. The elements of water.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.03,0:03:02.32,Default,Ice,0000,0000,0000,,Alchemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.91,0:03:04.91,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.66,0:03:09.00,Default,Ice,0000,0000,0000,,Sacrifices are inherent when attempting something great.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:11.16,Default,Ice,0000,0000,0000,,It's called the exchange of equivalences.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.16,0:03:14.84,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,This and that {\i1}aren't{\fscx30} {\r} the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.76,0:03:24.34,Default,Ice,0000,0000,0000,,Without a transmutation circle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.64,0:03:27.43,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You've got no time to be gawking!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.19,0:03:38.07,Default,Ice,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:39.36,Default,Ice,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:41.86,Default,Ice,0000,0000,0000,,It should have boiled if there was a drop of liquid in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.53,0:03:44.99,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You ruined my coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:48.37,Default,Ice,0000,0000,0000,,Auto-mail...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:56.34,Default,Ice,0000,0000,0000,,Genius alchemy skills that don't require transmutation circles...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.96,0:03:59.55,Default,Ice,0000,0000,0000,,...and an auto-mail as his right arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:01.05,Default,Ice,0000,0000,0000,,So you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:05.22,Default,Ice,0000,0000,0000,,...that Fullmetal Alchemist, Edward Elric!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:10.85,Default,Ice,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... that's not you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:12.31,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:14.81,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Alphonse, his younger brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.81,0:04:16.19,Default,Ice,0000,0000,0000,,So this runt is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.19,0:04:17.81,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling short?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.65,0:04:25.91,Default,Ice,0000,0000,0000,,To think that someone with the title of "Fullmetal Alchemist"...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:27.99,Default,Ice,0000,0000,0000,,...would be such a small child...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.62,0:04:30.16,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Quit calling me short!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:36.04,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, I don't think he was talking about your height.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:38.59,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I can't forgive him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.54,0:04:43.09,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,As expected from Edward Elric, the Fullmetal Alchemist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:46.09,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We appreciate your support.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:50.31,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, I'm his little brother, Alphonse Elric.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:53.39,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to make you wait, Al.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.39,0:04:54.60,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:57.60,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you're in such a rush...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:10.49,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Steam...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:12.08,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.91,0:05:15.08,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Damn him, using petty tricks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:19.46,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you underestimated your opponent, Fullmetal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:22.21,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:25.26,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I told you to listen up earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.05,0:05:28.55,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,But you claimed that you would be able to-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.51,0:05:31.10,Default-alt,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah, I get it. My mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.22,0:05:35.27,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,You should always listen to your seniors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.27,0:05:36.60,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.85,0:05:37.81,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,In any case...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.35,0:05:40.31,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Isaac McDougal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.77,0:05:45.49,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,He used to be a State Alchemist and was called Isaac of the Ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:46.65,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Used to?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.65,0:05:47.65,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.70,0:05:53.62,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,He performed outstandingly during\Nthe Ishbal War as a member of our army.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:06:02.79,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,He gave up his title of State Alchemist after the war and became involved in a dissident movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:05.80,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Capturing him is a top priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:08.72,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,But if circumstances dictate it, we may have to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.22,0:06:11.60,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:12.93,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Do as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.39,0:06:16.31,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,All we really want are results.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.60,0:06:21.31,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.61,0:06:24.52,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,have you found any clues on how to fix your body?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.03,0:06:28.53,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Like you'd give us time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.53,0:06:30.36,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.36,0:06:34.83,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,What a rough order, capturing the Ice Alchemist, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:37.54,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Or could this be a chance for a promotion?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.08,0:06:41.92,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Are you two perhaps... the Elric Brothers?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:47.55,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Oh man, I'm quite honored to be able to meet the youngest State Alchemist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.55,0:06:49.55,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Maes Hughes, a Lieutenant Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:53.39,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,U-Umm... I'm Alphonse Elric, the younger brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:56.85,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,What?! {\i1}That{\fscx30} {\r} one is the Fullmetal Alchemist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.85,0:06:59.31,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better not call me a shrimp...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:00.35,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Hughes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.35,0:07:01.23,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.23,0:07:03.40,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't have anything to do here, go home already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:05.73,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,I will, after I do what I need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.90,0:07:09.69,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,You guys probably haven't booked a place to stay yet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:11.57,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,If so, stay at my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:22.50,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,It's my wife, Gracia, and my daughter, Elicia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:26.13,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Elicia-chan~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:29.76,Default,Elicia,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, Daddy! Your beard hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:31.51,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.51,0:07:33.05,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Rub-rub-rub.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.05,0:07:34.14,Default,Elicia,0000,0000,0000,,Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.55,0:07:38.22,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Say hi to our guests, the Elric Brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:40.39,Default,Elicia,0000,0000,0000,,So tall!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.43,0:07:42.35,Default,Elicia,0000,0000,0000,,So short!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.73,0:07:47.07,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Elicia-chan, I'm Edward Elric.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:49.86,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,This is my {\i1}little{\r} brother, Alphonse Elric.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:52.99,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Understand? {\i1}Little{\r} brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.99,0:07:55.37,Default,Elicia,0000,0000,0000,,If you're the older one, how come you're so short?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.78,0:08:00.37,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, they're letting us stay. Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.37,0:08:03.46,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start dinner. Gracia is a great cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:08:01.29,Default-alt,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Lemme go! Lemme go, Al!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:08.30,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.30,0:08:09.50,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.92,0:08:11.92,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Itadakimasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.13,0:08:16.60,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It's so good! Wow, it tastes great!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:18.05,Default,Gracia,0000,0000,0000,,Eat a lot, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.05,0:08:18.68,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.39,0:08:23.44,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Alphonse, you can't eat with that armor on, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.52,0:08:26.77,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:29.82,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Al is... in the middle of an alchemy training right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.98,0:08:33.11,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Al. I'll eat for the both of us like always, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:35.57,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me, leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:35.57,Default-alt,Elicia,0000,0000,0000,,Training~ Training~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.66,0:08:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,586)\fad(600,0)\c&HFFFFFF&\2c&H000000&\shad1\bord2\fnDFPHSMincho-W9\fs40\b0}Central Prison
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.95,0:08:45.75,Default,Kimb,0000,0000,0000,,That's the funniest joke I've heard in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:50.34,Default,Kimb,0000,0000,0000,,Join forces with the Ice Alchemist?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.92,0:08:53.34,Default,Kimb,0000,0000,0000,,Me, the Crimson Alchemist?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:58.93,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,Kimbley, let's defeat Bradley\Nand the corrupt military, together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:03.81,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,I know you've seen it at Ishbal, too. That hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.81,0:09:07.90,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,You know what Bradley made us do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:11.36,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you killed those officers, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.49,0:09:15.45,Default,Kimb,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, please don't misunderstand me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:19.78,Default,Kimb,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't thinking of anything lofty like you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:21.37,Default,Kimb,0000,0000,0000,,The reason I killed them...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:24.37,Default,Kimb,0000,0000,0000,,...is because I wanted to. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:27.71,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,It's a shame, Kimbley.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.29,0:09:30.38,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,It really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:36.30,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:48.81,Default,Gracia,0000,0000,0000,,This is rare. You can't sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.81,0:09:49.94,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:56.78,Default,Gracia,0000,0000,0000,,Should I take a guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.40,0:09:59.74,Default,Gracia,0000,0000,0000,,You were thinking about those two, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:06.87,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,State Alchemists are called\Nthe "dogs of the military" by the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.37,0:10:10.67,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,When I think that he has to carry such a burden at such an age...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.34,0:10:17.30,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.47,0:10:22.22,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Gracia-san's quiche was just like Mom's, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:24.06,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it tasted great.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.06,0:10:24.81,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.81,0:10:28.94,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'd better add that to my\N"List of things to eat when I get my body back".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.15,0:10:32.44,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you'd better do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.32,0:10:34.27,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.27,0:10:35.28,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.28,0:10:37.74,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,It would be nice to get our bodies back to normal soon, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.90,0:10:40.03,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.74,0:10:47.12,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,Just one more...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.12,0:10:51.63,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,With just one more, Bradley will fall straight to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:03.72,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,According to reports, Isaac infiltrated Central Prison last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.72,0:11:07.47,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot let the situation continue any longer. Make sure you seek him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:11.44,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Block the roads and search everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:14.31,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,You are authorized to shoot him on sight for all I care.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.90,0:11:16.52,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,This is an order from the Führer President!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.19,0:11:21.70,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I... will be heading out, as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:23.57,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, relief soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.57,0:11:25.70,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Five casualties so far. Report to headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:27.08,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,This is horrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:28.95,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It was a steam explosion...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.95,0:11:32.79,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,If the temperature of water is raised rapidly, it expands explosively.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.79,0:11:35.42,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,A human body is 70% water, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:38.88,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry. We have to find that guy fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.88,0:11:39.63,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.38,0:11:43.26,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.93,0:11:50.98,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,To dodge my alchemy... As expected of you, Sir Isaac.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.98,0:11:53.19,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,That voice... Armstrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:55.02,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.07,0:12:01.61,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,The Strong Arm Alchemist,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:05.03,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Alex Louis Armstrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:05.95,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.95,0:12:11.75,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,High-pressure water slashes through a variety of things!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.04,0:12:17.79,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite meaningless against my fist, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.26,0:12:26.30,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Major!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.39,0:12:30.35,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.27,0:12:34.31,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Water from a canteen, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.31,0:12:35.73,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Al.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.40,0:12:38.19,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to go after him, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.19,0:12:40.32,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Elric Brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.32,0:12:41.11,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.32,0:12:41.11,Default-alt,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:50.58,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, Ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:54.79,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,Roy Mustang...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.79,0:12:57.75,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,...no, the Flame Alchemist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.75,0:13:01.63,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,It's a shame that I must fight a past comrade.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.63,0:13:05.05,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,Comrade? I do not have any friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.05,0:13:08.89,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,The only ones that were at Ishbal were the corrupted army and their dogs!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.31,0:13:19.11,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,It's just fire, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.11,0:13:20.57,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,It can't win against water!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.99,0:13:30.07,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.87,0:13:35.83,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,Good, good...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.83,0:13:36.83,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That's it for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:40.84,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering what the heck you were doing in an alley like this back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:42.05,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...so I came back, and bingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:46.84,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,No use trying to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.84,0:13:49.47,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,Run? There's no need for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.98,0:14:03.90,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,A simultaneous alchemy reaction... like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.90,0:14:05.40,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.94,0:14:07.90,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... could this be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.03,0:14:10.41,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The Philosopher's Stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.41,0:14:17.29,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:18.75,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It's freezing all of the moisture in the atmosphere...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.75,0:14:20.12,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,Edward Elric.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.88,0:14:23.80,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,Dog of the military. State Alchemist!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:27.76,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea what this country is trying to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.76,0:14:30.30,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hell if I know! More importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:34.31,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,If you {\i1}did{\fscx30} {\r} know, you'd understand why I'm doing this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.31,0:14:36.31,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.98,0:14:47.07,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Al, good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:49.20,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, his alchemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:49.90,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.90,0:14:50.91,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.91,0:14:53.20,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You have the philosopher's stone, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.62,0:14:55.20,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.20,0:14:57.45,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not going to tell me, then I'll {\i1}make{\r} you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.45,0:15:00.96,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really the time to be blabbering nonsense?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:14.47,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,A skill that has been passed down\Nthe Armstrong household for generations...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.72,0:15:16.47,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We're leaving it to you, Major!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.47,0:15:19.39,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Artistic Alchemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.39,0:15:21.98,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Engrave it on your soul!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.94,0:15:28.19,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.19,0:15:30.11,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing, Major?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.11,0:15:31.49,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:37.54,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,The wall of ice...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.54,0:15:39.08,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...is connecting....
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.08,0:15:40.71,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be... that man...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,0:15:45.71,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...is trying to freeze Central...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.42,0:15:48.63,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...no, Central Headquarters?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.21,0:15:53.09,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Major! Al and I will stop that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.47,0:15:55.09,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,While we're on that, please take care of the transmutation circles!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.09,0:15:57.47,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,I need to destroy them, right? Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:05.86,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,King Bradley! Now is finally the time for me to to send you to hell with my ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:06.90,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Now wait just a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:19.12,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.58,0:16:26.58,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hot! Hot! Hot! Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.75,0:16:29.05,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.50,0:16:30.51,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,Too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.18,0:16:34.76,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Al!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:46.69,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,An... empty armor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.98,0:16:52.40,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,You... established a soul on to a piece of armor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.28,0:16:55.07,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,Losing an arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:58.20,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,...and the little brother is left without a body...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.62,0:17:01.49,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,I get it now. You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.41,0:17:05.29,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,...committed taboo, didn't you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.75,0:17:09.75,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,The greatest taboo an alchemist can commit...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:12.26,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,Human Transmutation!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.63,0:17:17.55,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Al!!! Alphonse!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.55,0:17:20.30,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! This isn't how it was supposed to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.06,0:17:25.39,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!!! They took it away!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:29.69,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Give him back... He's my little brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.02,0:17:34.15,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Give him back... He's my only brother!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:45.37,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You... just took a step toward hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:05.81,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Just give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:07.81,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,There's no water for you to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:09.44,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,You've forgotten...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.44,0:18:12.57,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,...what 70% of the human body is made of!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.07,0:18:16.07,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.16,0:18:23.62,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,You guys don't know the true face of this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.25,0:18:36.34,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother... Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:39.01,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Al, we're going after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:43.01,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Using little tricks like these...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.14,0:18:47.18,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Did we do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:50.27,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.82,0:18:58.57,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare underestimate my flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.11,0:19:01.07,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.70,0:19:04.08,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your useless days to rainy days only, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.08,0:19:14.17,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,Bradley!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:23.43,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,Brace yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.84,0:20:06.30,Default,Kimb,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:09.93,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Major! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:13.81,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.54,0:20:37.79,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Führer President King Bradley...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.42,0:20:42.72,Default,Bradley,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, good work, Fullmetal Alchemist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.09,0:20:50.56,Default,Bradley,0000,0000,0000,,I now have something to brag to my son about, that I was able to lend you a helping hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.56,0:20:55.27,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,What, you've caught a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.27,0:20:58.52,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I heard you were great out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.52,0:21:01.69,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,All I did was destroy the transmutation circles.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:04.40,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,The Führer President defeated him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.40,0:21:07.82,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,And the Führer President is saying that it was your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.74,0:21:10.20,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,What, are you unsatisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:12.33,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Accept his words thankfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.33,0:21:13.79,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,You've always said this, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:16.96,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,"You should always listen to your seniors."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.21,0:21:26.43,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, we never found out whether he had a philosopher's stone or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.43,0:21:29.43,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we're going to have to wait for the investigation by the army.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.35,0:21:35.02,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Edward Elric, I heard you were hospitalized, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.02,0:21:36.10,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,...I came here right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.10,0:21:42.36,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Now, how about I comfort you while you're bored out of your mind from being hospitalized!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.03,0:21:47.53,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Don't they just bring warmth to your heart? These graceful muscles of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.53,0:21:49.70,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be shy, now. You can touch them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.16,0:21:53.33,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.00,0:22:00.00,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So Isaac died.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.00,0:22:03.17,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,He was a human pillar, too. That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.17,0:22:05.34,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,And? What about the philosopher's stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.51,0:22:09.09,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so he used it all up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.76,0:22:13.64,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,Gluttony, you're not supposed to be eating weird things.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.14,0:22:17.89,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's all going well in Lior.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.94,0:22:20.35,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,It will begin soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.27,0:22:23.32,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,Very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.16,0:24:01.54,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Resembul.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.25,0:24:07.13,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The kind town where the boys were born and spent their childhood with their mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.09,0:24:10.01,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Seeking for that smile that was lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.01,0:24:13.93,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,the boys commit taboo and witness the "truth".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.89,0:24:19.35,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Fullmetal Alchemist:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.35,0:24:21.64,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 2, The First Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.19,0:24:26.44,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It was his heart that decided to step out into the world.
